rganized into divisions once again. These divisions included the Public Health Division, Mental Health Division, Medical Services Insurance Division, and the Financial and Administrative Services Division. The Department of Health was replaced by the new Ministry of Health in 1972.\" .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#1924> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> \"1924\" .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Ontario.%20Dept.%20Of%20Health> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasBeginningDate> <ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#1924> .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/2025-10-13T07-28-22> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#imports> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#> .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#1972> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#Date> .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Status%3A%20Approved> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#RecordState> .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Authority%20Record%20Creation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Ontario.%20Dept.%20Of%20Health> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasEndDate> <ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#1972> .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#AA37> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> \"AA37\" .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#A%20Ontario%20Government%20Name> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> \"A Ontario Government Name\" .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Provincial%20Board%20Of%20Health%20Of%20Ontario> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Ontario.%20Dept.%20Of%20Health> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasOrHadAgentName> <ontology://generated-from-draw-