 by Mrs. Simcoe and a photograph of either one of her watercolours or a watercolour collected by her.\" .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#F%2047-11-1> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasIdentifierType> <ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Current%20Reference%20Code> .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Web%20Enabled%3A%20Y> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> \"Web Enabled: Y\" .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Elizabeth%20Simcoe%20Loose%20Sketches-i1> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#instantiationExtent> \"318 watercolours  58 drawings  8 prints  1 photograph\" .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#F%2047-11> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> \"F 47-11\" .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Elizabeth%20Simcoe%20Loose%20Sketches%20Archival%20Description> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> \"Elizabeth Simcoe loose sketches Archival Description\" .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Elizabeth%20Simcoe%20Loose%20Sketches> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasContentOfType> <ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Graphic%20Materials> .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Elizabeth%20Simcoe%20Loose%20Sketches%20Archival%20Description> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#hasRecordState> <ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Status%3A%20Approved> .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Sub-Series> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> \"Sub-Series\" .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Web%20Enabled%3A%20Y> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Elizabeth%20Simcoe%20Loose%20Sketches> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> \"Elizabeth Simcoe loose sketches\" .\n<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Elizabeth%20Simcoe%20Sketches> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .\n<o